                    "value": "\nTo be affected a device needs to be configured with at least one BGP peer and an import policy applicable to it which contains the respective match condition:\n\n[ protocols bgp group <group> neighbor <IP-address> ]\n[ protocols bgp ... import <policy-name> ]\n[ policy-options policy-statement <policy-name> term <term-name> from route-filter ...]\n\n"
