                            "value": "<p>The following software releases have been updated to resolve this specific issue:</p><p>Junos OS: 20.4R3-S8, 21.2R3-S2, 21.3R3-S5, 21.4R2-S1, 21.4R3-S5, 22.1R1, and all subsequent releases.</p><p>Junos OS Evolved: 20.4R3-S8-EVO, 21.2R3-S2-EVO, 21.4R2-S1-EVO, 21.4R3-S5-EVO, 22.1R1-EVO, and all subsequent releases.</p>"
